Package: ODEnetwork
Version: 1.3.2
Title: Network of Differential Equations
Description: Simulates a network of ordinary differential equations of
        order two. The package provides an easy interface to construct
        networks. In addition you are able to define different external
        triggers to manipulate the trajectory. The method is described
        by Surmann, Ligges, and Weihs (2014)
        <doi:10.1109/ENERGYCON.2014.6850482>.
